---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Use Cases" description="Real-world deployment patterns and use cases for the EDDI AI orchestration platform." fullWidth={true}>

<section class="uc-hero hero-gradient-bg">
	<div class="uc-hero-inner">
		<h1>Use Cases</h1>
		<p>Real-world deployment patterns for the EDDI platform.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<article class="uc-content">

<div class="uc-grid">
	<div class="uc-card">
		<span class="uc-icon">🏥</span>
		<h3>Healthcare</h3>
		<p>Patient intake agents, medical FAQ bots, appointment scheduling — with full audit trails for HIPAA compliance and EU AI Act readiness.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="uc-card">
		<span class="uc-icon">🏦</span>
		<h3>Financial Services</h3>
		<p>Customer support agents with compliance logging, fraud detection assistants, and internal knowledge base chatbots with cryptographic audit trails.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="uc-card">
		<span class="uc-icon">🛒</span>
		<h3>E-Commerce</h3>
		<p>Product recommendation agents, order support bots, and multi-language customer service — with intent-based routing across specialized agents.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="uc-card">
		<span class="uc-icon">🏭</span>
		<h3>Manufacturing</h3>
		<p>Equipment maintenance assistants, quality control agents, and supply chain optimization — running on-premises or in private clouds.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="uc-card">
		<span class="uc-icon">🏛️</span>
		<h3>Government</h3>
		<p>Citizen inquiry agents, internal process automation, and document analysis — in air-gapped environments with no cloud dependency.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="uc-card">
		<span class="uc-icon">🧑‍💻</span>
		<h3>Developer Platforms</h3>
		<p>Internal AI services for engineering teams — API-accessible agents that integrate into CI/CD pipelines, code review, and documentation workflows.</p>
	</div>
</div>

</article>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.uc-hero {
		padding: calc(var(--nav-height, 4rem) + 4rem) 1.5rem 3rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.uc-hero h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		color: var(--color-text);
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
	}

	.uc-hero p {
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.uc-content {
		max-width: 72rem;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem 1.5rem 6rem;
	}

	.uc-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(18rem, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.uc-card {
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	html[data-theme='dark'] .uc-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}
	html[data-theme='light'] .uc-card {
		background: #f5f6f8;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
	}

	.uc-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.uc-icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.uc-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-text);
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
	}

	.uc-card p {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}
</style>
